title: The Origins of Nike F.C.
description:
We are not a football team. 
We are a football club. 
We don't play football. 
We live it. 
We have no formation. 
No board of directors.
No main stand. 
We are a club for the fearless, for the brilliant. 
For the ones who know that without risk, there is no victory. 

We are Nike F.C. #nikefc
